    "form_header_text": "Rep. Friedman FY27 Programmatic/Language Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "This form will collect Fiscal Year 2027 appropriations requests for California's 30th Congressional District (only programmatic and language requests). Programmatic Request: a request to fund a specific program in the appropriations bill at a specified level. Language Request: a request to include specific bill or report language that does not direct funding to a particular entity but encourages, urges, or directs some type of action by an agency. If you are submitting multiple requests on behalf of your organization, please submit one form per request. Please submit requests at your earliest convenience. The deadline to submit an FY27 appropriations request to Rep Friedman's office is close of business (5pm EST) Friday, March 6. If you are experiencing technical issues with this form, please reach out to CA30.Appropriations@mail.house.gov.",
